overview: Dedi and Beno are two unemployed scholars. Incidentally there is a job opening as a morgue guard. Dedi could accept the job, but not for Beno. He's the type of cowardly guy. It was from the morgue that they met MAYA, a model. Maya received an inheritance from her grandfather who had just died mysteriously. The grandfather inherited the house and a very large plantation.
title: Setannya Kok Masih Ada
